com.wolvencraft.yasp.db.data.sync

Interface DataStore.NormalData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlocksData.TotalBlocksEntry, DeathsData.TotalDeathsEntry, ItemsData.TotalItemsEntry, PlayersData.DistancePlayers, PlayersData.MiscInfoPlayers, PlayersData.Players, PVEData.TotalPVEEntry, PVPData.TotalPVPEntry
    Enclosing interface:
    DataStore

    public static interface DataStore.NormalData
    Represents the "totals" of statistical data. These entries are changing every time their corresponding data type changes.
    No duplicate entries are allowed.
    Author:
    bitWolfy
